{
  "stem": "17135.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they were-- the husbands were-- were-- were Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or their wives were Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they worked in the local industries.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were semi-prisoners also, like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he told me, yeah, this true.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There is a-- Elly Diament is in-- in-- in Dantzic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How I got there-- how I got-- ah, I played dumb and deaf because the Russians, if you had a number and you speak only German, you are an SS man that made a number.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And first they shoot and then they ask questions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had to play a role.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I-- I played deaf and dumb.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never showed them that I'm-- that-- that I'm a refugee, that I'm a survivor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and-- and I got, at night, to Dantzic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at-- at the railway-- everything at the center of the town was the railway station.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because that was the only place that-- not-- even if it was destroyed, they rebuilt it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because it was important for communication.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were two Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They-- they were doing business with the Russians, hard currency.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Marks and dollars and-- and-- and-- and rubles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and-- and zloties.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was an agreement if you want to know if somebody is Jewish, you-- you said to him [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[HEBREW] means our-- our people, in-- in-- in Yiddish, in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I ask one guy that looked like a real shrewd, shrewd merchant.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was dealing and wheeling, and dealing, don't ask me, with everybody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He said, I don't know about your sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I know where the committee-- we call it the committee, the-- the Jewish committee, where it is.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It must have been three o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And let me tell you something.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
